title: DIAWI upload fails with `Error [ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND]: Cannot find package 'form-data'`
body:
# Problem

iOS pipeline stage failed a couple of times for https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/18276 
with error :  

```
[2023-12-22T17:03:42.749Z] + nix-shell --show-trace --run 
'./scripts/diawi-upload.mjs StatusIm-Mobile-231222-165804-884266-pr18276.ipa' 
--impure --no-out-link --keep DIAWI_TOKEN --option sandbox relaxed --attr 
shells.default /Users/jenkins/workspace/status-mobile_prs_ios_PR-18276/default.nix

[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z] node:internal/errors:490
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     ErrorCaptureStackTrace(err);
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     ^
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z] 
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z] Error [ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND]: Cannot find package 'form-data' imported from 
/Users/jenkins/workspace/status-mobile_prs_ios_PR-18276/scripts/diawi-upload.mjs
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     at new NodeError (node:internal/errors:399:5)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     at packageResolve (node:internal/modules/esm/resolve:889:9)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     at moduleResolve (node:internal/modules/esm/resolve:938:20)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     at defaultResolve (node:internal/modules/esm/resolve:1153:11)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     at nextResolve (node:internal/modules/esm/loader:163:28)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.503Z]     at ESMLoader.resolve (node:internal/modules/esm/loader:838:30)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.504Z]     at ESMLoader.getModuleJob (node:internal/modules/esm/loader:424:18)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.504Z]     at ModuleWrap.<anonymous> (node:internal/modules/esm/module_job:77:40)
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.504Z]     at link (node:internal/modules/esm/module_job:76:36) {
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.504Z]   code: 'ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND'
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.504Z] }
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.504Z] 
[2023-12-22T17:03:45.504Z] Node.js v18.16.0

script returned exit code 1
```
Although I only saw this issue on this PR and no other PR, which seems weird.
